title: BigFish Games - Rescue at Rajini Island - New Hidden Object Puzz
description:
Rescue at Rajini Island  


Embark on an epic adventure into the unknown as you search for Captain Walsh and his missing crew 
of adventurers; lost on an uncharted Island. Explore ancient ruins and search for evidence of a 
lost civilization. Gather diary entries from the crew and un-scramble foreign symbols and 
engravings as you follow a path of clues...but toward what answer? Find out for yourself in this 

addictive Hidden Object masterpiece!
Engaging game-play
Beautiful Hidden Object scenes
Explore the unknown!
